==English==

===Pronunciation===
*:Rhymes: [[Rhymes:English:-æbɪn|-æbɪn]]

===Noun===
{{en-noun}}
# {{US}} A remote, primative dwelling, often built of [[log]]s, as with the place Abraham Lincoln was born: '''a small crudely constructed dwelling'''.
# A [[compartment]] on land.
# A room on a passenger ship.
# The passenger area of an airplane.

